arStrings.szText: They have surrounded us. I'm sure not what or who summoned the demons here, but they overwhelmed us in the mine in mere moments. I tried to run, but stumbled over loose rocks. Now my cursed leg is broken.
I can hear the echoes of other people still alive, but I can't see them. I suppose it doesn't matter. As long as the demons can’t see me, I’m safe.
